title: War of the Roses: He Didn't Hang Up the Phone
description: Missy was on the phone with her husband recently and when the conversation ended he didn't hang up and she could hear him having a conversation with another woman.  When she confronted him, he claimed it was just the radio she heard, but to her, it felt like an in person convo.  Was he with someone, and if so, was he doing something bad?
